en_142270_0	The presentation of the ordinance to declare Sri Pada as a sacred area was held at the Sri Pada Raja Maha Vihare, Galpottawala.
en_142270_1	Former President Maithripala Sirisena presided over the presentation of the Sannaspathra which declares Sri Pada as a sacred area.
en_142270_2	The Sannaspathra was presented to the Chief Incumbent of the Sri Pada Vihare the Ven.
en_142270_3	Bengamuwe Dhammadinna Thera.
en_142270_4	A ‘Sannaspathra’ to make the Maha Saman Devalaya a sacred area was also presented.
en_142270_5	It was handed over to Basnayake Nilame Migara Jayasundara.
